Description (描述):

HalfTrend is a trend-following technical analysis tool designed to identify market direction, entry/exit signals, and trend strength. It utilizes color-coded lines—Blue for Bullish and Red for Bearish—combined with slope analysis and arrows to visualize opportunities.

Core Features:

Trend Identification: Blue lines indicate bullish trends; Red lines indicate bearish trends.

Buy/Sell Signals: Arrows appear at trend reversals (Up for Long, Down for Short).

Customizable Sensitivity: Adjust "Amplitude" and "Channel Deviation" to suit various market volatilities.

Best Practices:

Designed for trend-following strategies.

Recommended to use alongside RSI or MACD to filter noise.

Works across Stocks, Crypto, and Forex on all timeframes.
